name: CircularFifoQueue_peekTest
description: Unit tests for the peek functionality of the CircularFifoQueue class.

test_cases.name: testPeekOnEmptyQueue
test_cases.description: Tests the peek functionality on an empty queue, expecting a null result.

test_cases.name: testPeekOnNonEmptyQueue
test_cases.description: Tests the peek functionality on a non-empty queue, expecting the first added element.

test_cases.name: testPeekAfterAddingElements
test_cases.description: Tests the peek functionality after adding elements to the queue, expecting the first added element and then the next after the queue wraps around.

test_cases.name: testPeekAfterRemovingElements
test_cases.description: Tests the peek functionality after removing elements from the queue, expecting the next element in the queue.

test_cases.name: testPeekAfterClearingQueue
test_cases.description: Tests the peek functionality after clearing the queue, expecting a null result.
